%% Pudel Slash Command Flow v2.0.0

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Discord User
    participant Discord as Discord API
    participant JDA as JDA 6
    participant Listener as InteractionEventListener
    participant Manager as InteractionManagerImpl
    participant Handler as @SlashCommand Handler
    participant Brain as PudelBrain (optional)

    Note over User,Brain: Slash Command Execution Flow

    User->>Discord: /command [options]
    Discord->>JDA: SlashCommandInteractionEvent
    JDA->>Listener: onSlashCommandInteraction()

    Listener->>Manager: handleSlashCommand(event)
    Manager->>Manager: Lookup registered handler<br/>(by command name)

    alt Handler Found
        Manager->>Handler: handle(event)

        alt Simple Response
            Handler->>Discord: event.reply("Response")
            Discord->>User: Show response
        else AI-Powered Response
            Handler->>Brain: process(message)
            Brain->>Brain: Analyze intent
            Brain->>Brain: Apply personality
            Brain-->>Handler: Generated response
            Handler->>Discord: event.reply(response)
            Discord->>User: Show AI response
        else Deferred Response
            Handler->>Discord: event.deferReply()
            Discord->>User: "Bot is thinking..."
            Handler->>Handler: Long operation
            Handler->>Discord: event.getHook().editOriginal("Done!")
            Discord->>User: Update message
        end
    else Handler Not Found
        Manager->>Discord: event.reply("Unknown command").ephemeral()
        Discord->>User: Show error (ephemeral)
    end

    Note over User,Brain: Registration (happens at plugin enable)

    rect rgb(40, 60, 40)
        Note right of Handler: @SlashCommand annotation<br/>automatically registered by<br/>PluginAnnotationProcessor
    end
